      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry — the same geometry used in the COU. Operating conditions span the clinical CPB range (2.5–7.0 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM). Blood analog fluid properties match clinical blood viscosity. High geometric and operational similarity supports direct transfer of validation evidence to COU."
